' ============================================================
' 关系连线
' ============================================================

' --- 注解应用 ---
AiTool ..> ToolHandler : marks classes
ToolParam ..> ToolHandler : marks fields

' --- 框架内部关系 ---
ToolRegistry --> ToolHandler : holds references
ToolRegistry *--> AiToolMeta : builds metadata
AiToolMeta *-- AiToolMeta.ToolParamMeta
ToolExecutor --> ToolRegistry : looks up
ToolExecutor --> ToolHandler : calls
ToolExecutor ..> ToolContext : receives
ToolExecutor ..> ToolResult : returns
ToolExecutor ..> AiAuditLog : writes

' --- 权限桥接 ---
AiPermissionBridge --> ToolExecutor : injects PermissionChecker
AiPermissionBridge --> AuthService : delegates

' --- 所有工具实现 ToolHandler ---
CreateBomTool ..|> ToolHandler
SearchBomTool ..|> ToolHandler
SearchEquipmentTool ..|> ToolHandler
GetEquipmentDetailTool ..|> ToolHandler
AddEquipmentFunctionTool ..|> ToolHandler
UpdateEquipmentFunctionTool ..|> ToolHandler
DeleteEquipmentFunctionTool ..|> ToolHandler
QueryPlanStatusTool ..|> ToolHandler
QueryOrderStatusTool ..|> ToolHandler
QueryWorkOrderStatusTool ..|> ToolHandler
SearchLineTool ..|> ToolHandler
SearchProcessTool ..|> ToolHandler
SearchWorkStepTool ..|> ToolHandler
AddWorkStepTool ..|> ToolHandler
SearchTeamTool ..|> ToolHandler

' --- 工具依赖业务 Service ---
CreateBomTool --> bomService : calls
SearchBomTool --> bomService : calls
SearchEquipmentTool --> equipmentService : calls
GetEquipmentDetailTool --> equipmentService : calls
AddEquipmentFunctionTool --> equipmentService : calls
UpdateEquipmentFunctionTool --> equipmentService : calls
DeleteEquipmentFunctionTool --> equipmentService : calls
QueryPlanStatusTool --> planService : calls
QueryOrderStatusTool --> orderService : calls
QueryWorkOrderStatusTool --> workOrderService : calls
SearchLineTool --> lineService : calls
SearchProcessTool --> processFlowService : calls
SearchWorkStepTool --> workStepService : calls
AddWorkStepTool --> workStepService : calls
SearchTeamTool --> teamService : calls

